                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Tables begin with 1663 (5423) in cycle 286, and of the cycles 287 to 293 complete tables are given; the two latter cycles have been inserted later before folio 158. There are number of notes in the margin, accompanying the cycles. </p>
                     
                     
                     
